# Data Mapping Template

## Salesforce to SUNation CRM Field Mapping

### Account Object Mapping
| Salesforce Field | SF API Name | SF Type | SUNation Field | SN API Name | SN Type | Notes |
|------------------|-------------|---------|----------------|-------------|---------|-------|
| Account Name | Name | Text(255) | Account Name | name | text | Required |
| Account Number | AccountNumber | Text(40) | Account Number | account_number | text | |
| Type | Type | Picklist | Type | type | text | Map picklist values |
| Industry | Industry | Picklist | Industry | industry | text | Map picklist values |
| Annual Revenue | AnnualRevenue | Currency | Annual Revenue | annual_revenue | numeric | |
| Number of Employees | NumberOfEmployees | Number | Employee Count | employee_count | integer | |
| Phone | Phone | Phone | Phone | phone | text | |
| Website | Website | URL | Website | website | text | |
| Billing Address | BillingAddress | Address | Billing Address | billing_address | jsonb | Convert to JSON |
| Shipping Address | ShippingAddress | Address | Shipping Address | shipping_address | jsonb | Convert to JSON |

### Contact Object Mapping
| Salesforce Field | SF API Name | SF Type | SUNation Field | SN API Name | SN Type | Notes |
|------------------|-------------|---------|----------------|-------------|---------|-------|
| First Name | FirstName | Text(40) | First Name | first_name | text | Required |
| Last Name | LastName | Text(80) | Last Name | last_name | text | Required |
| Email | Email | Email | Email | email | text | |
| Phone | Phone | Phone | Phone | phone | text | |
| Mobile Phone | MobilePhone | Phone | Mobile | mobile | text | |
| Title | Title | Text(128) | Title | title | text | |
| Department | Department | Text(80) | Department | department | text | |
| Mailing Address | MailingAddress | Address | Mailing Address | mailing_address | jsonb | Convert to JSON |

### Opportunity Object Mapping
| Salesforce Field | SF API Name | SF Type | SUNation Field | SN API Name | SN Type | Notes |
|------------------|-------------|---------|----------------|-------------|---------|-------|
| Opportunity Name | Name | Text(120) | Name | name | text | Required |
| Amount | Amount | Currency | Amount | amount | numeric | |
| Stage | StageName | Picklist | Stage | stage | enum | Map to enum values |
| Probability | Probability | Percent | Probability | probability | integer | |
| Close Date | CloseDate | Date | Close Date | close_date | date | |
| Next Step | NextStep | Text(255) | Next Step | next_step | text | |
| Description | Description | Long Text | Description | description | text | |
| Lead Source | LeadSource | Picklist | Lead Source | lead_source | text | |

### Custom Fields Template
| Object | SF Field Label | SF API Name | SF Type | Business Purpose | SUNation Mapping | Migration Notes |
|--------|----------------|-------------|---------|------------------|------------------|-----------------|
| Account | Solar Capacity | Solar_Capacity__c | Number | Track installation size | custom_fields | Create custom field |
| Account | Installation Date | Install_Date__c | Date | Track go-live date | custom_fields | Create custom field |
| Opportunity | System Size | System_Size__c | Number | Solar system size | custom_fields | Create custom field |
| Contact | Decision Maker | Decision_Maker__c | Checkbox | Identify key contacts | custom_fields | Create custom field |